description:
The Today Show's Jenn Falik and I teamed up this holiday season to give you more of what you've been asking for: GIFT GUIDES! We go through all of our favorite things and pick the best of the best. This week we're talking about what the tweens want (TikTok things), and the best gifts for our partners that we can eventually take back for ourselves.


Shop the Tween gift guide:
